style=\"color: #808080;\"><i><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span lang=\"en-US\">Departure from Hotel: 8h00</span></span></i></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<p align=\"justify\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\"><i><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span lang=\"en-US\">Panoramic view of Matanzas City</span></span></i></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<p align=\"justify\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\"><i><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span lang=\"en-US\">Short stop at Bacunayagua lookout (Highest bridge of Cuba 112m)</span></span></i></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<p align=\"justify\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\"><i><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span lang=\"en-US\">Visit the Christ of Havana</span></span></i></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<p align=\"justify\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\"><i><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span lang=\"en-US\">Visit to a cigar Factory (Optional and upon availability)</span></span></i></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<p align=\"justify\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\"><i><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span lang=\"en-US\">Visit the Revolution Square</span></span></i></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<p align=\"justify\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\"><i><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span lang=\"en-US\">Cuban lunch at a Paladar (Private Restaurant) Not included</span></span></i></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<p align=\"justify\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\"><i><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span lang=\"en-US\">Panoramic view of the Presidents’ Avenue</span></span></i></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<p align=\"justify\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\"><i><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span lang=\"en-US\">Panoramic view or walk through downtown Old Havana, including Fraternity Park, The Capitol building, the Great Theater of Havana, Central Park with its surrounding hotels, both National and Universal Museums of Fine Arts and the Museum of the Revolution.</span></span></i></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<p al